2) Palladium Futures Contract Rules: 100.02, "Contract Unit"; 100.03, "Grad=
e=20
and Quality Specification"; 100.04, "Packaging and Marking"; 100.08 "Delive=
ry=20
Procedure"; 100.10, "Depository Receipt"; 100.11, "Inspection"; 100.14,=20
